webpackJsonp([0x900713e16110],{580:function(o,e){o.exports={pathContext:{docHtml:'<h1>Tool Detection</h1>\n<p>The tool used to build an application is detected as follows:</p>\n<p>If a specific tool is explicitly configured, then that tool is selected to create your application\'s manifests.</p>\n<p>If not, then the tool is detected implicitly as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ksonnet</strong> if there are two files, one named <code>app.yaml</code> and one named <code>components/params.libsonnet</code>.</li>\n<li><strong>Helm</strong> if there\'s a file matching <code>Chart.yaml</code>. </li>\n<li><strong>Kustomize</strong> if there\'s a <code>kustomization.yaml</code>, <code>kustomization.yml</code>, or <code>Kustomization</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Otherwise it is assumed to be a plain <strong>directory</strong> application. </p>\n<h2>References</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://github.com/argoproj/argo-cd/blob/master/reposerver/repository/repository.go#L286">reposerver/repository/repository.go/GetAppSourceType</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://github.com/argoproj/argo-cd/blob/master/server/repository/repository.go#L97">server/repository/repository.go/listAppTypes</a></li>\n</ul>',docPath:"argo-cd/docs/user-guide/tool_detection",proj:"argo-cd"}}}});
